## Problem
- Cache system exists but not used in CLI
- No question -> cache check -> AI -> cache save structure
- Memory storage disabled
- Inefficient due to AI calls on every query

## Changes
1. Added cache check (start of process_with_full_pipeline)
   - Check cache on question input
   - Return response immediately on cache hit
   - Run full pipeline on cache miss

2. Added cache save (after response generation)
   - Save AI response to cache
   - Use cached response on next identical question

3. Enabled memory storage
   - Re-enabled previously disabled memory storage
   - Added user info extraction functionality
   - Added user info search from memory

## Structure Change
Before:
Question -> Intent -> Agents -> AI -> Response

After:
Question -> Cache Check -> (Hit) Return Response
                    -> (Miss) Intent -> Agents -> AI -> Response -> Cache Save

